text: @GovMurphy Thanks @GovMurphy for the @NJGov numbers. Another point re higher mortality for #COVID19 compared to annual flu: that’s occurred during drastic #StayHomeSavesLives measures. Deaths would be spiking even higher if we behaved like it’s “just the flu”.
